## DESCRIPTION
##   Find Coefficients for a Maclaurin Series
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## Tagged by nhamblet

## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Infinite sequences and series)
## DBsection(Representations of functions as series)
## Date(6/3/2002)
